27:21.596 --> 27:22.858
- So it's time.

27:22.902 --> 27:24.425
- For what?

27:24.468 --> 27:26.645
- No, no, no, the common thread
between everyone.

27:26.688 --> 27:31.084
All the inefficiencies
and the, you know, complaints

27:31.127 --> 27:32.607
